name: Santa Claus
description:
Also known as Father Christmas, Saint Nicholas, or simply Santa, is a legendary character originating in Eastern Christian culture who is said to bring children gifts on Christmas.
He is said to accomplish this with the aid of Christmas elves, who make the toys in his workshop at the North Pole, and flying reindeer who pull his sleigh through the air.

#065 Exclusive piece from the event "Box2Burn 02" X-mas Edition
